{
  "stem": "17526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And there were rumors that there's new territories being prepared for them and they're going to be given new lodgings and it's a war and this is near the front and people are getting killed in the war, Germans are getting killed and Poles are getting killed, therefore we have to clear out these cities.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We knew very well that these people are being hauled away to no return places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Next door to us, the father and mother were taken away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There were a bunch of kids, young and older kids, about five or six kids, and the father and mother were selected.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I mean, the kids came home to the apartment and-- and-- and it was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And this went on for days until we-- really, it soaked in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It really made us aware that we are doomed to-- to extinction, to-- to really being done away with.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But we just couldn't get-- we couldn't-- we just could not believe that this is really happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And this went on and on, but this big selection was the real final jolt for us to realize it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It was right after this here that this friend of mine that I started talking before insisted that I go with him and join up the underground.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I was afraid, as I said before, and I stayed back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He went and we later found out that there-- this was a trap that was put on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And there was about 100 or so, or 200-- it was a big group of young people who had the courage and guts to try to go into the underground.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they were shot like dogs in the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
